            <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD refers to Mivart’s <hi rend="italic">On the genesis of species</hi> (Mivart 1871a; see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7447.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from St G. J. Mivart, 19 January 1871</ref>).</note>
